re%20from%20India%20who%20had%20to%20deal%20with%20vagaries%20of%20politics%20and%20statecraft%2C%20akin%20to%20present%20day%2C%20more%20than%202300%20years.%20King%20Ashoka%20stood%20tall%20among%20not%20only%20his%20peers%20but%20in%20world%20history%20on%20several%20fronts.%20His%20emphasis%20on%20public%20health%20by%20building%20area%20hospitals%2C%20planting%20shaded%20trees%20along%20highways%20and%20even%20veterinary%20hospitals%20for%20wounded%20horses%20and%20elephants%20is%20unparalleled%20in%20the%20history%20of%20world%20kings.%20Compare%20that%20with%20the%20Nero-esque%20apathy%20displayed%20by%20our%20prime%20minister%20to%20the%20indescribable%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtonpost.com%2Fworld%2Fasia_pacific%2Findia-coronavirus-lockdown-migrant-workers%2F2020%2F03%2F27%2Fa62df166-6f7d-11ea-a156-0048b62cdb51_story.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eplight%20of%20our%20very%20own%20daily-wage%20laborers%20(dehumanigingly%20labelled%20%E2%80%9Cmigrant%E2%80%9D%20workers)%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%3Cspan%3E%20when%20they%20had%20to%20walk%20hundreds%20of%20kilometres%20to%20their%20homes%20due%20to%20the%20sudden%20lockdown%20imposed%20by%20the%20shock-and-awe%20specialist%20in%20the%20early%20days%20of%20COVID-19%20pandemic.%20The%20world%20should%20be%20glad%20that%20there%20was%20no%20other%20international%20leader%20that%20took%20a%20leaf%20out%20of%20Vishwaguru%E2%80%99s%20book%20in%20that%20regard.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFast-forward%20about%20two%20thousand%20years%20in%20to%20the%201500s%2C%20Emperor%20Akbar%20is%20another%20Indian%20leader%20that%20achieved%20world%20fame%20for%20his%20deeds.%20To%20focus%20on%20just%20one%20pertinent%20aspect%2C%20he%20took%20secularism%2C%20an%20ideal%20implemented%20already%20by%20the%20likes%20of%20Ashoka%2C%20to%20new%20heights%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fhome%2Fsunday-times%2Fdeep-focus%2Fhow-akbar-went-from-great-to-not-so-great%2Farticleshow%2F47402293.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eby%20pro-actively%20encouraging%20tolerance%20of%20all%20faiths%20in%20a%20world%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20was%20already%20ravaged%20by%20religious%20wars.%20From%20India%2C%20he%20set%20a%20bright%20example%20for%20other%20kings%20and%20rulers%20across%20the%20world%20to%20follow%20and%20emulate.%20Our%20current%20dispensation%20can%20certainly%20learn%20a%20lesson%20or%20two%20on%20tolerance%20rather%20than%20literally%20bulldozing%20everyone%20else%20that%20does%20not%20fit%20the%20unabashed%20rightwing%20bill.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EComing%20to%20the%20modern%20Indian%20nation%20state%2C%20our%20first%20prime%20minister%2C%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%2C%20attained%20Vishwaguru%20status%20in%20the%201950s%20and%20%E2%80%9960s%20by%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.britannica.com%2Ftopic%2FNon-Aligned-Movement%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Espearheading%20the%20non-aligned%20movement%20in%20a%20world%20that%20was%20reeling%20under%20unprecedented%20devastation%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20heaped%20by%20nuclear%20warfare%2C%20holocaust%2C%20world%20war%20II%20and%20the%20Korean%20war.%20He%20collaborated%20with%20other%20world%20leaders%20from%20Egypt%2C%20Yugoslavia%2C%20Ghana%20and%20Indonesia%20in%20setting%20up%20a%20group%20that%20staunchly%20opposed%20expansionist%20wars.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAlthough%20most%20revisionist%20individuals%20have%20discredited%20Nehru%20for%20his%20non-aligned%20stance%20in%20the%20aftermath%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20embrace%20of%20so-called%20economic%20liberalisation%20in%20the%201990s%2C%20it%20is%20indisputable%20that%20such%20a%20stand%20was%20the%20most%20humanitarian%20one%20to%20take%20for%20continuing%20the%20legacy%20of%20peace%20propagation%20from%20our%20history%20dating%20back%20to%20Buddha%20and%20Ashoka.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EToday%2C%20in%202024%2C%2