20Muslims%20constitute%20one%20of%20the%20most%20marginalised%20social%20groups.%20Besides%20being%20looked%20down%20with%20condescension%20as%20%E2%80%98outsiders%E2%80%99%2C%20they%20are%20stereotyped%20as%20%E2%80%9CBangladeshi%E2%80%9D%2C%20%E2%80%9Cillegal%20immigrant%E2%80%9D%20and%20even%20%E2%80%9CJihadi%E2%80%9D.%20Their%20citizenship%20is%20persistently%20under%20attack%2C%20and%20they%20are%20targeted%20through%20the%20state%20power%20through%20mechanisms%20such%20as%20the%20National%20Register%20of%20Citizens%2C%20and%20issues%20such%20as%20eviction%20and%20%E2%80%9Cdoubtful%20voters%E2%80%9D.%20A%20lot%20of%20human%20rights%20violations%20against%20Assam%20Muslims%20are%20already%20in%20the%20public%20domain.%20In%20this%20article%2C%20I%20will%20specifically%20deal%20with%20the%20question%20of%20representation%20vis-a-vis%20Muslims%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMuslims%20of%20Assam%20are%20a%20heterogeneous%20category%2C%20who%20are%20sub-divided%20into%20Miya%20Muslims%2C%20Goriya%2C%20Moria%2C%20Julha%2C%20Deshi%2C%20Bihari%20Muslims%2C%20Muslims%20of%20Barak%20Valley%2C%20etc.%20The%20ruling%20parties%20in%20the%20state%20have%20been%20sharpening%20the%20existing%20faultlines%20amongst%20Muslim%20groups%20in%20the%20state.%20Some%20Muslim%20groups%20like%20Goriya%2C%20Moria%2C%20Julha%2C%20Deshi%2C%20Syed%2C%20etc.%2C%20are%20arbitrarily%20termed%20as%20%E2%80%98indigenous%E2%80%99%20by%20the%20government%20of%20Assam%20only%20to%20exclude%20the%20Miya%20Muslims%20from%20the%20public%20and%20political%20spheres.%20Miya%20Muslims%20are%20arguably%20the%20most%20discriminated%20and%20excluded%20category%20in%20the%20state.%20But%20in%20this%20article%2C%20I%20will%20briefly%20discuss%20the%20total%20discrimination%20against%20Muslims%20in%20the%20state%2C%20in%20general%2C%20by%20looking%20at%20the%20question%20of%20representation%20of%20the%20community%20in%20the%20major%20public%20institutions%2C%20on%20which%20the%20government%20is%20clearly%20silent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fdetention-criminalisation-statelessness-the-aftermath-of-assams-nrc%5C%22%3EDetention%2C%20Criminalisation%2C%20Statelessness%3A%20The%20Aftermath%20of%20Assam%E2%80%99s%20NRC%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAbysmal%20representation%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAssam%20has%20about%2035%25%20Muslim%20population%2C%20and%20the%20representation%20of%20this%20community%20in%20government%20offices%20is%20abysmally%20low.%20Presently%2C%20there%20are%2016%20ministers%20in%20the%20state%20government%2C%20and%20none%20of%20them%20is%20a%20Muslim.%20The%20state%20has%2034%20districts%20and%20not%20even%20a%20single%20district%20has%20a%20Muslim%20deputy%20commissioner%20(DC).%20In%20these%2034%20districts%2C%20not%20even%20a%20single%20superintendent%20of%20police%20(SP)%20is%20a%20Muslim.%20The%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fghconline.gov.in%2Findex.php%2Fhonble-the-chief-justice-sitting-judges%2F%5C%22%3EGauhati%20high%20court%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%2023%20judges%2C%20including%20one%20chief%20justice%C2%A0and%20surprisingly%20none%20of%20them%20is%20a%20Muslim.%20These%20discriminations%20are%20not%20only%20limited%20to%20administration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPresently%2C%20after%20the%202021%20assembly%20election%2C%20the%20state%20has%2031%20Muslim%20MLAs%20out%20of%20126%20MLAs.%20The%20share%20amounts%20to%2024.60%25%20of%20the%20total%20MLAs.%20But%20a%20proportionate%20number%20would%20be%2043%20Muslim%20MLAs%20in%20the%20Assam%20state%20assembly.%20In%20the%202016%20assembly%20elections%2C%2029%20Muslim%20MLAs%20were%20elected%2C%20which%20amounts%20to%2023.02%25%20representation.%20Thanks%20to%20the%20delimitation%20of%20the%20constituencies%20in%20the%20state%2C%20at%20least%20none%20Muslim%20MLA%20seats%20will%20be%20further%20lost%20in%20the%20next%20assembly%20election.%20The%20state%20presently%20has%20two%20Muslim%20MPs%20out%20of%2014%20MPs%2C%20meaning%20only%2014.29%25%20Muslim%20representation%20among%20the%20MPs.%20Not%20to%20mention%2C%20the%20number%20of%20MPs%2C%20which%20will%20be%20representative%20of%20the%20Muslim%20population%20in%20the%20state%2C%20is%20five.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F01%2F27162618%2FIMG_2018.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F01%2F27162618%2FIMG_2018.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F01%2F27162618%2FIMG_2018-300x169.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F01%2F27162618%2FIMG_2018-1024x576.jpeg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-578102%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22675%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EIllustration%3A%20Pariplab%20Chakraborty%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAssam%20has%20two%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fhighereducation.assam.gov.in%2Fportlets%2Fprofiles-of-universities-and-colleges%5C%22%3Ecentral%20universities%20and%2014%20state%20universities%3C%2Fa%3E.%20I%20have%20taken%20a%20sample%20of%20five%20universities%20to%20see%20the%20representation%20of%20Muslims%20in%20the%20teaching%20positions%20from%20their%20respective%20website%2C%20in%20these%20universities.%20One%20of%20these%20universities%20is%20a%20central%20university%20(Tezpur%20University)%2C%20and%20the%20other%20four%20are%20state%20universities.%20Out%20of%20the%20four%20state%20universities%2C%20I%20have%20included%20one%20recently%20opened%20university%20(BSSR%20University)%20and%20the%20oldest%20university%20in%20the%20region%20(Gauhati%20University).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETezpur%20Central%20University%20has%20a%20representation%20of%20Muslim%20teachers%20of%203.98%25%2C%20while%20Gauhati%20University%20has%20Muslim%20teachers%20of%207.47%25.%20Arabic%20and%20Parsi%20departments%20of%20the%20Gauhati%20University%20alone%20have%20seven%20Muslim%20teachers%2C%20and%20without%20these%20two%20departments%2C%20the%20representation%20of%20Muslim%20teachers%20in%20the%20University%20comes%20down%20to%205.54%25.%20Bodoland%20University%2C%20located%20in%20the%20Bodoland%20Territorial%20Region%20(BTR)%20of%20Assam%2C%20does%20not%20have%20a%20single%20Muslim%20teacher%20out%20of%20the%2093%20teachers%20the%20university%20has.%20Another%20relatively%20old%20university%20in%20the%20state%2C%20Dibrugarh%20University%2C%20which%20was%20established%20in%201965%2C%20has%20about%202.44%25%20of%20its%20teachers%20Muslim%2C%20which%20is%20abysmally%20low.%20BSSR%20Vishwavidyalaya%20is%20a%20newly%20opened%20university%20in%20the%20Golaghat%20district%20of%20the%20state%20with%205.88%25%20of%20Muslim%20teachers.%20All%20these%20clearly%20show%20severely%20less%20representation%20of%20Muslims%20in%20the%20university%20system%20than%20their%20population%20share%20in%20the%20state%2C%20which%20is%20about%2035%25.%20Representation%20of%20Muslims%20in%20the%20media%20houses%20in%20the%20state%20is%20either%20abysmally%20low%20or%20entirely%20missing.%20This%20underrepresentation%20is%20not%20an%20overnight%20phenomenon%2C%20for%20it%20happened%20over%20the%20decades%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ctable%3E%5Cn%3Ctbody%3E%5Cn%3Ctr%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%20width%3D%5C%2247%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ESl.%20No.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%20width%3D%5C%22196%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EName%20of%20the%20University%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%20width%3D%5C%22125%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ETotal%20number%20of%20teachers%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%20width%3D%5C%22125%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ENumber%20of%20Muslim%20teachers%20(Permanent%20positions)%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%20width%3D%5C%22108%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EPerc