0investment%20of%20Rs%204%2C000%20crore%20to%20improve%20the%20economic%20condition%20of%20rural%20women.%20To%20benefit%20from%20this%20scheme%2C%20women%20cannot%20have%20more%20than%20three%20children%20except%20in%20Scheduled%20Tribes%20(ST)%20and%20Scheduled%20Castes%20(SC).%20Women%20in%20the%20SC%20and%20ST%20categories%20can%20benefit%20from%20this%20scheme%20even%20if%20they%20have%20four%20children.%20Notably%2C%20the%20Sachar%20committee%20clarifies%20that%20the%20economic%20condition%20of%20Muslims%20is%20worse%20than%20that%20of%20SCs%20and%20STs.%20And%20in%20a%20time%20when%20no%20one%20wants%20to%20have%20more%20children%2C%20it%20is%20the%20poorest%20sections%20of%20all%20communities%20that%20have%20relatively%20more%20children.%20Mary%20E%20John%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fopinion%2Fcolumns%2Fassam-government-new-schemes-discrimination-communalisation-not-justice-9111255%2F%5C%22%3Ecritiques%3C%2Fa%3E%20this%20move%20of%20the%20government%20and%20argues%20that%20this%20scheme%20is%20to%20exclude%20Muslim%20women%20who%20are%20more%20marginalised.%C2%A0%20Another%20scheme%2C%20namely%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fother-states%2Fassam-chief-minister-is-communalising-land-settlement-scheme-aiudf%2Farticle66144465.ece%5C%22%3EVasundhara%202.0%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20through%20which%20land%20rights%20are%20given%20to%20landless%20people%20of%20the%20state%2C%20too%20excludes%20Muslims%20totally.%20There%20are%20many%20such%20examples.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%C2%A0Overwhelming%20number%20of%20Muslims%20as%20undertrials%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20contrary%2C%20the%20share%20of%20Muslims%20in%20the%20jails%20of%20the%20state%20throws%20a%20very%20interesting%20picture.%20As%20per%20Prison%20Statistics%20India%202022%2C%20published%20by%20the%20National%20Crimes%20Record%20Bureau%20(NCRB)%2C%2055.6%25%20of%20convicts%20lodged%20in%20the%20prisons%20of%20Assam%20are%20Muslims.%20When%20it%20comes%20to%20undertrials%20lodged%20in%20the%20jails%2C%2052.54%25%20of%20them%20are%20Muslims%20in%20Assam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20the%20above%20discussion%2C%20it%20is%20clear%20that%20discrimination%20and%20exclusion%20are%20visible%20in%20Assam.%20Muslims%20in%20Assam%20are%20excluded%20from%20decision-making%2C%20politics%2C%20and%20various%20institutions%2C%20including%20institutions%20of%20higher%20learning%20and%20administration.%20They%20are%20purposely%20and%20systematically%20made%20voiceless%20regarding%20policy%20formation%20and%20problem-raising.%20An%20exhaustive%20study%20to%20understand%20the%20discrimination%20and%20underrepresentation%20of%20Muslims%20in%20public%20life%20in%20the%20state%20is%20the%20urgent%20need%20of%20the%20hour.%20The%20situation%20is%20all%20the%20more%20alarming%20as%20Abdur%20Rahman%20writes%20in%20his%20book%20%3Cem%3EAbsent%20in%20Politics%20and%20Power%2C%20Political%20Exclusion%20of%20Indian%20Muslims%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20BJP%20openly%20portrays%20itself%20as%20anti-Muslim%20and%20has%20been%20against%20all%20forms%20of%20their%20empowerment.%20By%20depriving%20them%20of%20a%20just%20and%20equitable%20share%20in%20education%2C%20economy%20and%20politics%2C%20the%20party%20intends%20to%20push%20them%20into%20becoming%20second%20class%20citizens%E2%80%9D%20(p.97).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%20in%20Assam%2C%20the%20word%20discrimination%20is%20meaningless%20if%20the%20discrimination%20against%20Muslims%20is%20not%20considered.%20While%20other%20discriminated%20social%20groups%20enjoy%20the%20benefit%20of%20reservation%2C%20most%20of%20the%20Muslims%20in%20the%20state%2C%20especially%20the%20Miya%20Muslims%20of%20the%20state%2C%20do%20not%20have%20any%20reservation%20to%20make%20inroads%20into%20the%20system.%20They%20are%20always%20pushed%20to%20the%20margin%20to%20struggle%20for%20basic%20survival%20%E2%80%93%20food%2C%20clothes%2C%20and%20land.%20The%20picture%20of%20missing%20Muslims%20from%20public%20institutions%20is%20completely%20contradictory%20to%20the%20claim%2C%20%3Cem%3Esabke%20saath%20sabka%20bikas%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKeeping%20a%20community%20away%20from%20the%20positions%20of%20power%20in%20government-run%20institutions%20leads%20to%20stereotyping%20of%20the%20community.%C2%A0%20It%20is%20the%20need%20of%20the%20hour%20to%20bring%20Muslims%20of%20Assam%20into%20a%20suitable%20reservation%20system%20in%20the%20line%20of%20Scheduled%20Caste%20(SC)%20to%20ensure%20proportionate%20representation%20of%20this%20community%20in%20the%20social%2C%20political%2C%20economic%2C%20and%20educational%20positions%20and%20to%20ensure%20social%20justice%20to%20this%20marginalised%20community.%20The%20constitution%20of%20India%20promised%20equal%20opportunity%20for%20all%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20citizens%2C%20and%20it%20is%20time%20to%20deliver%20this%20promise%20to%20these%20marginalised%20citizens%20of%20peripheral%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ENazimuddin%20Siddique%20teaches%20Sociology%20at%20Jamia%20Millia%20Islamia%2C%20New%20Delhi.%20He%20can%20be%20contacted%20at%20sid.nazimuddin%40gmail.com.%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706183199000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F06%2F21151635%2FScreen-Shot-2021-06-21-at-3.16.21-PM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fwhither-assam-muslims-the-story-of-groups-exclusion-from-political-public-spheres%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Muslims%2C%20who%20constitute%2035%25%20of%20the%20state%20population%2C%20are%20abysmally%20represented%20in%20the%20positions%20of%20power.%20Their%20share%2C%20however%2C%20among%20the%20undertrials%20in%20the%20state%20in%2052.54%25.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fwhither-assam-muslims-the-story-of-groups-exclusion-from-political-public-spheres%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22