%2C%20two%20key%20leaders%20%E2%80%93%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20and%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%E2%80%93%20have%20ruled%20out%20any%20alliance%20with%20the%20Congress%20in%20Bengal%20and%20Punjab.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Mr%20Kumar%2C%2072%2C%20this%20would%20be%20the%20fifth%20change%20in%20camp.%20Since%202013%2C%20he%20has%20been%20swinging%20between%20the%20NDA%20and%20the%20mahagathbandhan%2C%20all%20the%20while%20keeping%20his%20job%20in%20the%20state%20intact.%C2%A0%20He%20switched%20sides%20last%20in%202022%20%E2%80%93%20barely%20two%20years%20after%20he%20had%20walked%20out%20of%20the%20Grand%20Alliance%20and%20joined%20the%20NDA.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20signs%20have%20all%20been%20there%20over%20the%20last%20weeks%2C%20with%20Mr%20Kumar's%20comments%20on%20dynastic%20politics%20and%20the%20subsequent%20retort%20from%20Lalu%20Yadav's%20daughter%20expanding%20the%20rift.%20Yesterday%2C%20his%20lack%20of%20response%20to%20the%20Congress%20invite%20for%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Yatra%2C%20put%20a%20question%20mark%20on%20his%20appearance.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Bharat%20Ratna%20for%20former%20Bihar%20Chief%20Minister%20Karpoori%20Thakur%20appears%20to%20have%20been%20a%20turning%20point%20scripted%20in%20advance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20said%20Mr%20Kumar%20has%20been%20upset%20over%20the%20lack%20of%20clarity%20in%20INDIA%20bloc's%20poll%20preparations%20and%20being%20passed%20over%20as%20a%20possible%20Prime%20Ministerial%20candidate.%20The%20delays%20to%20seat-sharing%20talks%20for%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20had%20been%20a%20further%20aggravation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706181360000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-04%2Fm2qhajq8_opposition-meet_625x300_12_April_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnitish-kumar-may-exit-alliance-in-bihar-likely-to-go-with-bjp-again-sources-4929675%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20INDIA%20bloc%20appears%20to%20be%20unravelling%20as%20a%20third%20key%20leader%20--%20Bihar%20Chief%20Minister%20Nitish%20Kumar%20--%20is%20likely%20to%20change%20camp%20again.%20Sources%20said%20it%20is%20likely%20that%20Mr%20Kumar%2C%20in%20a%20last-minute%20U-turn%20will%20partner%20with%20the%20BJP%20in%20the%20coming%20Lok%20Sabha%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnitish-kumar-may-exit-alliance-in-bihar-likely-to-go-with-bjp-again-sources-4929675%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnitish-kumar-may-exit-alliance-in-bihar-likely-to-go-with-bjp-again-sources-4929675%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnitish-kumar-may-exit-alliance-in-bihar-likely-to-go-with-bjp-again-sources-4929675%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22INDIA%20Ally%20Nitish%20Kumar%20Won't%20Join%20Rahul%20Gandhi's%20Yatra%20In%20Bihar%3A%20Sources%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EBihar%20Chief%20Minister%20Nitish%20Kumar%20will%20not%20join%20the%20Congress'%20'Bharat%20Jodo%20Nyay%20Yatra'%20when%20it%20enters%20his%20state%20on%20January%2030%2C%20sources%20said%20Thursday%20afternoon.%20Sources%20said%20an%20invitation%20was%20extended%20last%20evening%20-%20via%20the%20Congress'%20legislature%20party%20leader%20Shakeel%20Ahmad%20Khan%20but%20Nitish%20Kumar%2C%20already%20upset%20by%20delays%20to%20seat-sharing%20talks%20for%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20poll%2C%20was%20non-committal%20about%20his%20participation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20snub%20comes%20three%20days%20after%20the%20Congress'%20Bihar%20unit%20said%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20%26quot%3Bhad%20agreed%26quot%3B%20to%20appear%20at%20a%20rally%20in%20Purnia%20district.%20%26quot%3BIn%20the%20event%20of%20his%20getting%20caught%20elsewhere%2C%20he%20assured%20(us)%20a%20senior%20leader%20will%20be%20sent%20to%20represent%20his%20party%2C%26quot%3B%20senior%20Bihar%20Congress%20leader%20Chandra%20Mishra