ts%20with%20the%20Congress.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20latest%20(and%20potentially%20biggest)%20challenge%20comes%20a%20day%20after%20Bengal%20Chief%20Minister%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20all%20but%20cut%20ties%20with%20the%20bloc%2C%20insisting%20her%20Trinamool%20will%20fight%20all%2042%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20in%20the%20state%20under%20its%20own%20steam.%20Ominously%2C%20she%20also%20suggested%20she%20is%20reviewing%20her%20INDIA%20membership.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Banerjee%2C%20who%20will%20not%20participate%20in%20the%20yatra%20either%2C%20ripped%20into%20the%20Congress%20this%20week%2C%20accusing%20the%20party%20of%20failing%20to%20observe%20common%20courtesy%20by%20notifying%20her%20when%20the%20procession%20entered%20her%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELike%20Nitish%20Kumar%2C%20the%20fiery%20Trinamool%20boss%20has%20also%20criticised%20the%20Congress%20for%20dragging%20its%20feet%20over%20seat-sharing%20talks%3B%20the%20Congress%20reportedly%20wants%2010-12%20seats%20in%20Bengal%20but%20has%20been%20offered%20only%20two.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Banerjee's%20offer%2C%20sources%20have%20said%2C%20is%20based%20on%20the%20Congress'%20abysmal%20performance%20in%20the%20past%20two%20general%20elections%3B%20in%20the%202014%20poll%20the%20party%20won%20four%20seats%20and%2C%20five%20years%2C%20later%20won%20just%20two%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%2C%20aware%20its%20INDIA%20bloc%20experiment%20is%20on%20the%20brink%20of%20collapse%2C%20reached%20out%20immediately.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EComms%20boss%20Jairam%20Ramesh%2C%20with%20Mr%20Gandhi%20and%20the%20yatra%2C%20insisted%20%26quot%3Ball%20INDIA%20partners%20will%20unitedly%20fight%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20in%20Bengal%26quot%3B%2C%20and%20General%20Secretary%20KC%20Venugopal%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThere%20will%20be%20an%20alliance%20in%20Bengal...%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20is%20a%20serious%20leader%20in%20INDIA%20alliance.%20These%20are%20small%20differences.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706181180000%2C%22