the%20same%20amount%20of%20money%20that%20I%20made%20seven%20years%20ago%2C%26quot%3B%20Robert%20said.%20%26quot%3BA%20lot%20of%20things%20are%20getting%20more%20expensive%2C%20so%20it's%20costing%20more%20money%20for%20everything%2C%20which%20makes%20it%20harder.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EScreenshots%20shared%20with%20BI%20show%20Robert%20made%20%2452%20and%20%2458%20gross%20in%20about%20four%20hours%20on%20two%20recent%20mornings.%20He%20said%20over%20the%20past%20few%20months%2C%20he's%20noticed%20significantly%20more%20drivers%20on%20the%20road%2C%20which%20has%20made%20finding%20profitable%20rides%20more%20difficult.%20He%20also%20said%20it's%20challenging%20to%20assess%20which%20rides%20to%20accept%20when%20he%20has%20just%20a%20few%20seconds%20to%20decide%20and%20can't%20see%20the%20upfront%20fare%2C%20just%20the%20distance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20lot%20of%20times%20I%20have%20to%20accept%20every%20ride%20because%20they%20allow%20you%2015%20seconds%20to%20figure%20out%20whether%20that's%20going%20to%20be%20profitable%20for%20you%2C%26quot%3B%20Robert%20said%2C%20adding%20he%20recently%20got%20a%20ride%20that%20was%2014%20minutes%20away%20for%20a%20four-minute%20ride.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20getting%20to%20the%20point%20now%20where%20you%20really%20have%20to%20judge%20the%20rides%20and%20whether%20they're%20heading%20in%20your%20direction%2C%20or%20if%20you%20get%20a%20long%20ride%2C%20what%20are%20you%20going%20to%20do%20on%20the%20way%20back%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EFending%20for%20himself%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdriving-for-uber-lyft-retirement-gig-workers-delivery-driver-rideshare-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edriver%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20a%20disability%2C%20Robert%20said%20he's%20been%20concerned%20about%20his%20ratings%2C%20especially%20after%20a%20few%20recent%20one-star%20ratings%20from%20passengers.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.shrut