e%2C%20and%20if%20you're%20not%20doing%20customer%20service%20with%20their%20rides%2C%20they're%20not%20responsible%20for%20the%20bad%20ratings.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERobert%20said%20he%20recently%20joined%20a%20union%20of%20gig%20drivers%20in%20his%20area%20to%20get%20more%20protections%2C%20such%20as%20more%20backing%20in%20case%20he%20gets%20deactivated%20or%20falsely%20accused%20of%20anything.%20He%20said%20his%20union%20is%20also%20advocating%20for%20higher%20pay%2C%20as%20average%20Oregon%20rates%20are%20lower%20than%20Washington%20rates%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20to%20deal%20with%20the%20pain%20of%20what%20I've%20got%20now%2C%20and%20there's%20nothing%20much%20I%20can%20do%20about%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Robert%20said.%20%26quot%3BI'm%20kind%20of%20stuck%20in%20what%20I'm%20doing%2C%20it's%20out%20of%20my%20control.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAre%20you%20a%20gig%20driver%20who%20is%20struggling%20to%20make%20ends%20meet%3F%20Are%20you%20a%20gig%20driver%20with%20a%20disability%20looking%20for%20other%20types%20of%20work%3F%20Reach%20out%20to%20this%20reporter%20at%20%3Cu%3Ensheidlower%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fu%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdriving-for-uber-lyft-disability-stock-portland-cost-of-living-2024-1%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706180881000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65b15646617029e90a600db3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdriving-for-uber-lyft-disability-stock-portland-cost-of-living-2024-1%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Robert%2C%2056%2C%20drives%20for%20Uber%20and%20Lyft%20but%20said%20he%20has%20no%20other%20options%20to%20supplement%20his%20disability%20benefits%2C%20driving%20six%20days%20a%20week.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22nsheidlower%40insider.com%20(Noah%20Sheidlower)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A36%2C%22ca