20nation%2C%20rendering%20the%20asking%20of%20questions%20both%20superfluous%20and%C2%A0%20unbecoming.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20behind%20this%20agenda%20and%20persuasion%20lies%20ever-burgeoning%20private%20%C2%A0corporate%20wealth%20is%20by%20now%20acknowledged%20even%20by%20those%20who%20used%20to%20have%20some%20qualms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20to%20state%20institutions%20as%20well%2C%20India%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9Cmainstream%E2%80%9D%20media%2C%20nine%20out%20of%20ten%2C%20finds%20the%20victims%20in%20the%20wrong%20%C2%A0rather%20than%20the%20%C2%A0shamelessly%20%C2%A0partial%20agencies%20who%20tailor%20investigative%20energies%20to%20suit%20the%C2%A0%20faces%20they%C2%A0%20pick.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20such%20a%20context%2C%20the%20political%20opposition%2C%20their%20sound%20bytes%20notwithstanding%2C%20do%20seem%20insufficiently%20cognizant%20of%20the%20peril%20that%20awaits%20the%20republic.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENot%20many%20in%20the%20dispersed%20opposition%20%C2%A0actually%20seem%20to%20%C2%A0%C2%A0embrace%20the%20%C2%A0likelihood%20outlined%20above%2C%20namely%20that%20losing%20the%20next%20general%20election%C2%A0%20may%20not%20be%20just%20another%20normative%20electoral%20%C2%A0happening%2C%20but%20one%20%C2%A0that%20may%20in%20double%20quick%20time%20lead%20to%20a%20formal%20jettisoning%20of%20the%20basic%20verities%20of%20the%20Constitution%20with%20all%20the%20consequences%20that%20must%20follow.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20well%20to%20recognise%20that%20the%20bulk%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20new%20elite%20will%20have%20few%20qualms%20should%20such%20a%20transformation%20be%20attempted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20anything%2C%20they%20may%20applaud%20the%20deed%20to%20the%20echo%20which%20will%20applaud%20back%20(to%20borrow%20from%20the%20Bard).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20always%20the%20downtrodden%20who%20have%20the%20highest%20stake%20in%20an%20emancipatory%20constitutional%20order%2C%20and%20in%20a%20fair%20application%20of%20the%20regime%20of%20laws%2C%20not%20having%20friendly%C2%A0access%20to%20centres%20of%20entrenched%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20being%20so%2C%20the%20opposition%20might%20do%20well%C2%A0%20not%20just%20to%20do%20lip%20service%20to%20the%20need%20for%20democracy%20%C2%A0%C2%A0but%20internalize%20that%20need%20sufficiently%20in%20the%20coming%C2%A0%20days%20to%20formulate%20a%20common%20programme%20of%20action%20which%C2%A0%20finds%20credibility%20among%20the%20%C2%A0republic%E2%80%99s%20overwhelming%C2%A0%20majority%20of%20the%20dispossessed%2C%20persuasive%20enough%20to%20draw%20them%20away%20from%20the%C2%A0%20opium%20now%20so%20preponderant.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20that%20context%2C%20the%20significance%20of%20the%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Nyay%20Yatra%20cannot%20be%C2%A0%20overstated.%C2%A0%20Nor%20the%20mass%20contact%20programmes%20intended%20to%20be%20mounted%20by%20non-Congress%20opposition%20parties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20political%20task%20of%20confronting%C2%A0%20a%20mesmerised%20populace%20with%20the%20weight%20of%20reality%20and%20rationality%20is%20not%20an%20easy%20one%3B%20but%20it%20is%20a%20praxis%20that%20must%20be%20undertaken%C2%A0%20with%20a%20do%20or%20die%20conviction%2C%20and%20to%20the%20exclusion%20of%20fissiparous%20sectarian%20interests.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDemocracy%20cannot%20reside%20in%20the%20oracular%20voice%20of%20any%20one%20man%2C%20great%20or%20not.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Fbadri-raina%5C%22%3EBadri%20Raina%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0taught%20at%20Delhi%20University.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20piece%20was%20first%20published%20on%20The%20India%20Cable%20%E2%80%93%20a%20premium%20newsletter%20from%20The%20Wire%20%26amp%3B%20Galileo%20Ideas%20%E2%80%93%20and%20has%20been%20updated%20and%20republished%20here.%20To%20subscribe%20to%20The%20India%20Cable%2C%20click%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Ftheindiacable.com%2F%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%2