es%2C%20dementia%2C%20acute%20kidney%20injury%2C%20and%20hepatic%20ischemia.%20Orthostatic%20hypotension%2C%20a%20drop%20in%20blood%20pressure%20upon%20standing%2C%20is%20linked%20to%20a%20higher%20risk%20of%20falls.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22MAITREE%20BARAL%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Flife-style%2Fhealth-fitness%2Fhealth-news%2Fwhat-happens-when-bp-falls-doctor-explains-the-potential-risks%2Farticleshow%2F107144802.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BThank%20You%2C%20Mann%20Sahab%26quot%3B%3A%20Punjab%20Congress%20Leader%20To%20NDTV%20On%20AAP's%20Solo%20Plan%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20day%20after%20Punjab%20Chief%20Minister%20Bhagwant%20Mann%20revealed%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party's%20(AAP)%20plans%20to%20go%20solo%20in%20Punjab%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%2C%20one%20of%20the%20state's%20top%20Congress%20leaders%20has%20'thanked'%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20and%20said%20this%20is%20%26quot%3Bexactly%20what%20we%20wanted%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20what%20the%20Congress%20cadre%20in%20Punjab%20wanted%20from%20the%20beginning.%20There%20is%20a%20difference%20between%20Punjab%20and%20other%20states.%20Here%2C%20they%20(AAP)%20are%20in%20the%20government%20and%20we%20are%20the%20principal%20opposition.%20How%20can%20both%20of%20us%20get%20together%2C%26quot%3B%20Partap%20Singh%20Bajwa%2C%20Leader%20of%20Opposition%20in%20Punjab%20Assembly%2C%20told%20NDTV%20in%20an%20exclusive%20interview.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20we%20get%20together%2C%20the%20anti-incumbency%20vote%20is%20going%20to%20shift%2C%20either%20to%20the%20BJP%20or%20to%20the%20Akali%20Dal.%20How%20can%20we%20relinquish%20our%20position%3F%20Congress%20is%20on%20the%20comeback%20train.%20This%20way%2C%20we%20will%20finish%20our%20existence.%20We%20have%20to%20preserve%20our%20vote%20bank%2C%20and%20build%20on%20it.%20This%20is%20much%20better%20for%20both%20(Congress%20and%20AAP)%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Bajwa%20said%20that%20the%20seats%20the%20AAP%20and%20Congress%20win%20will%20remain%20with%20the%20anti-BJP%20Opposition%20bloc%20anyway.%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20fighting%20(AAP)%20in%20the%20Vidhan%20Sabha%20and%20outside%20it.%20Every%20day%2C%20the%20main%20opposition%20is%20coming%20from%20the%20Congress.%20We%20are%20on%20the%20streets%20of%20Punjab%20against%20them.%20How%20do%20you%20think%20we%20can%20sit%20on%20the%20same%20stage%20with%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20leader%20said%20this%20is%20not%20his%20stand%20alone.%20%26quot%3BEvery%20single%20Congress%20worker%20(feels%20the%20same).%20Our%20general%20secretary%20has%20been%20holding%20meetings%20with%20Congress%20workers%2C%20block%20president%2C%20district%20president%2C%20MLAs%20and%20former%20MLAs%2C%20MPs%20and%20former%20MPs%2C%20state%20party%20presidents.%2099.9%20per%20cent%20of%20people%20with%20folded%20hands%20have%20suggested%20that%20we%20would%20have%20nothing%20to%20do%20with%20AAP.%C2%A0%26quot%3BI%20would%20like%20to%20thank%20Mr%20Mann%2C%20he%20has%20made%20our%20job%20a%20little%20easier.%20This%20is%20exactly%20what%20we%20wanted%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20denied%20that%20such%20statements%20were%20part%20of%20bargaining%20tactics.%20%26quot%3BIf%20our%20votes%20shift%20to%20another%20party%2C%20they%20won't%20come%20back%20during%20the%202027%20Assembly%20polls.%20We%20have%20already%20seen%20such%20experiments%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20and%20Delhi.%20In%20Delhi%2C%20we%20helped%20these%20AAP%20guys%20to%20form%20their%20government%20in%202014.%20Since%20then%2C%20we%20are%20nowhere%20to%20be%20seen.%20We%20don't%20want%20a%20similar%20situation%20in%20Punjab%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Mann%20yesterday%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fafter-mamata-banerjee-aap-says-no-alliance-wit