(January%2024)%20again%20adjourned%20the%20hearing%20on%20student%20leader%20Umar%20Khalid%E2%80%99s%20bail%20plea.%20Khalid%20was%20arrested%20in%20September%202020%2C%20in%20connection%20with%20Unlawful%20Activities%20(Prevention)%20Act%20a%20case%20relating%20to%20the%20North-East%20Delhi%20communal%20violence%20in%20February%20that%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20bench%20of%20Justices%20Bela%20Trivedi%20and%20Ujjal%20Bhuyan%20was%20hearing%20Khalid%E2%80%99s%20special%20leave%20petition%20challenging%20the%20Delhi%20high%20court%E2%80%99s%20decision%20to%20deny%20him%20bail%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livelaw.in%2Ftop-stories%2Fsupreme-court-umar-khalid-delhi-riots-larger-conspiracy-bail-247542%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ELivelaw%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Khalid%20has%20also%20filed%20a%20writ%20petition%20challenging%20various%20provisions%20under%20the%20UAPA.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20hearing%20was%20reportedly%20adjourned%20on%20Wednesday%20because%20Justice%20Trivedi%20had%20to%20be%20in%20a%20different%20special%20bench%20combination%20to%20hear%20another%20matter.%20The%20matter%20has%20now%20been%20listed%20for%20January%2031%2C%20with%20Justice%20Trivedi%20saying%20it%20would%20be%20%E2%80%9Chigh%20on%20the%20board%E2%80%9D%20on%20that%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKhalid%E2%80%99s%20bail%20plea%20hearing%20has%20now%20seen%20multiple%20delays%20and%20adjournments.%20His%C2%A0prayer%20for%20bail%20was%20rejected%20by%20a%20trial%20court%20in%20Delhi%20in%20March%202022.%20He%20then%20moved%20the%20Delhi%20high%20court%20in%20October%202022%2C%20which%20upheld%20the%20trial%20court%20order.%20The%20student%20leader%20then%20approached%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20in%20May%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20matter%20came%20up%20before%20the%20apex%20court%20for%20the%20first%20time%20on%20May%2018%2C%202023%20it%20was%20adjourned%20twice%2C%20once%20on%20July%2012%2C%202023%20after%20the%20Delhi%20Police%20sought%20more%20time%20to%20file%20a