t%20was%20one%20Mr%20Shettar%20claimed%20in%20three%20successive%20Assembly%20elections%20between%202008%20and%202018.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20blamed%20his%20loss%20on%20%26quot%3Bmoney%20power%20and%20pressure%20tactics%26quot%3B%20and%20accused%20his%20BJP%20rival%20of%20%26quot%3Bdistributing%20Rs%20500%20and%20Rs%201%2C000%20(notes)%26quot%3B%20to%20voters.%20%26quot%3BIn%20the%20last%20six%20elections%20I%20have%20not%20at%20all%20used%20money%20power...%20never%20distributed%20money%20to%20voters.%20(This%20is%20the)%20first%20time%20a%20BJP%20candidate%20distributed%20Rs%20500-Rs%201000...%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fjagadish-shettar-karnataka-results-money-factor-pressure-tactics-congress-heavyweight-on-huge-poll-upset-4033094%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETop%20BJP%20Defector%20Jagadish%20Shettar's%20Accusation%20After%20Karnataka%20Results%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Wednesday%2C%20as%20rumours%20swirled%20of%20Mr%20Shettar's%20return%20to%20the%20BJP%2C%20the%20Congress'%20DK%20Shivakumar%20accused%20the%20saffron%20party%20of%20%26quot%3Bdesperation%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BMany%20BJP%20leaders%20are%20desperately%20trying%20for%20the%20return%20of%20Shettar%20who%20is%20with%20the%20Congress%20now.%20This%20is%20a%20tell-tale%20sign%20of%20weakness...%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20at%20a%20Mysuru%20event.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20don't%20have%20candidates%20for%20the%20upcoming%20general%20elections%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Shivakumar%20continued.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJagadish%20Shettar%20is%20seen%20as%20an%20influential%20member%20of%20the%20powerful%20Lingayat%20community%2C%20which%20accounts%20for%20nearly%2017%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20population.%20This%20makes%20their%20support%20crucial%20for%20any%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-ne