%20of%20seats%2C%20the%20Trinamool%20Congress%20will%20very%20much%20be%20a%20part%20of%20the%20front%20that%20believes%20and%20fights%20for%20the%20Constitution%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20O'Brien%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrinamool%20sources%20have%20told%20NDTV%20that%20Mr%20Chowdhury%20was%20the%20%26quot%3Bgravedigger%26quot%3B%20of%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20in%20Bengal.%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20because%20of%20him%20and%20his%20daily%20rant%20that%20things%20have%20fallen%20flat.%20After%20the%20Chief%20Minister's%20byte%20yesterday%2C%20they%20(Congress)%20are%20getting%20into%20damage%20control.%20It%20is%20too%20late%20now%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20Trinamool%20source%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20source%20added%20that%20the%20Trinamool%20%26quot%3Bwas%20very%20patient%26quot%3B%20during%20the%20seat-sharing%20negotiations.%20%26quot%3BWe%20were%20gracious%20enough.%20But%20all%20we%20saw%20was%20delay%2C%20delay%20and%20delay%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20source%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20remarks%20that%20sent%20the%20Congress%20leadership%20back%20to%20the%20drawing%20board%2C%20Ms%20Banerjee%20yesterday%20announced%20that%20Trinamool%20would%20fight%20solo%20in%20Bengal%20and%20take%20a%20decision%20on%20any%20alliance%20with%20the%20Congress%20only%20after%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20has%20since%20been%20in%20damage%20control%20mode%2C%20assuring%20the%20strained%20ties%20would%20be%20mended.%20Senior%20party%20leader%20Jairam%20Ramesh%20has%20said%20they%20will%20find%20a%20%26quot%3Bsolution%20to%20the%20impasse%26quot%3B.%20Mr%20Ramesh%20had%20yesterday%20said%20the%20Congress%20%26quot%3Bcannot%20imagine%20INDIA%20bloc%20without%20Mamataji%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECongress%20MP%20Rahul%20Gandhi%2C%20whose%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Nyay%20Yatra%20entered%20Bengal%20today%2C%20said%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20will%20fight%20injustice.%C2%A0%26quot%3BI%20am%20happy%20to%20have%20come%20to%20West%20Bengal.%20We%20have%20come%20here%20to%20listen%20to%20you%20and%20stand%20with%20you.%20BJP-RSS%20are%20spreading%20hatred%2C%20violence%20and%20injustice.%20So%2C%20INDIA%20formation%20is%20going%20to%20fight%20anyay%20(injustice)%20together%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Banerjee's%20remarks%20on%20the%20alliance%20had%20come%20after%20talks%20on%20sharing%20seats%20hit%20a%20roadblock.%20According%20to%20reports%2C%20the%20Trinamool%20was%20offering%20two%20seats%20to%20the%20Congress%20in%20Bengal%2C%20but%20the%20latter%20wanted%20at%20least%2010.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMatters%20reached%20a%20tipping%20point%20when%20Mr%20Chowdhury%2C%20also%20the%20Congress's%20leader%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20called%20the%20Trinamool%20chief%20an%20%26quot%3Bopportunist%26quot%3B%20leader%20and%20said%20the%20Congress%20is%20capable%20of%20contesting%20polls%20on%20its%20own.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20Trinamool%20and%20the%20Congress%20leadership%20showing%20a%20united%20front%20at%20INDIA%20meetings%2C%20Mr%20Chowdhury%20lost%20no%20opportunity%20to%20target%20Ms%20Banerjee%20at%20the%20state%20level.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20public%20remarks%20against%20the%20Trinamool%20supremo%20recently%20prompted%20Congress%20leader%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20to%20intervene.%20%26quot%3BMamata%20Banerjee%20is%20very%20close%20to%20me%20and%20our%20party.%20Sometimes%20our%20leaders%20say%20something%2C%20their%20leaders%20say%20something%2C%20and%20it%20goes%20on.%20It's%20a%20natural%20thing.%20Such%20comments%20won't%20matter%20and%20these%20are%20not%20things%20that%20are%20going%20to%20disrupt%20things%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Gandhi%20had%20earlier%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrinamool's%20hard%20bargaining%20in%20seat-sharing%20must%20be%20seen%20as%20a%20common%20push%20by%20regional%20forces%2C%20including%20AAP%20and%20Samajwadi%20Party%2C%20for%20a%20greater%20role%20in%20their%20strongholds.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706173320000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com