cial%20media%20confused.%20However%2C%20the%20decision%20was%20correct%20because%20of%20the%20rule%20that%20the%20International%20Cricket%20Council%20(ICC)%20has%20for%20such%20scenarios.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20pacer%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Jasprit%20Bumrah%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F1724-jasprit-bumrah-playerprofile%5C%22%3EJasprit%20Bumrah%3C%2Fa%3E%20bowled%20a%20full%20toss%20on%20the%20pads%20and%20it%20was%20flicked%20behind%20square%20on%20the%20on-side%20by%20Rehan.%20The%20throw%20from%20the%20fielder%20was%20a%20wide%20one%20and%20it%20beat%20the%20backup%20fielder%20and%20went%20straight%20to%20the%20boundary.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInitially%2C%206%20runs%20were%20awarded%20to%20Rehan%20but%20the%20umpire%20reversed%20his%20decision%20and%20said%20only%205%20runs%20would%20be%20given%20as%20the%20two%20batters%20hadn't%20crossed%20each%20other%20when%20the%20throw%20left%20the%20hand%20of%20the%20fielder.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20rule%20was%20seriously%20looked%20upon%20after%20a%20similar%20incident%20took%20place%20in%20the%20England%20vs%20New%20Zealand%20ODI%20World%20Cup%20final%202019.%20In%20that%20instance%2C%20England%20were%20given%206%20runs%20instead%20of%205%20even%20though%20the%20two%20batters%20hadn't%20crossed%20each%20other.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20does%20the%20rule%20say%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMCC%20rule%2019.8%20is%20applicable%20on%20the%20matter.%20It%20says%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E19.8%20Overthrow%20or%20wilful%20act%20of%20fielder%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIf%20the%20boundary%20results%20from%20an%20overthrow%20or%20from%20the%20wilful%20act%20of%20a%20fielder%2C%20the%20runs%20scored%20shall%20be%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3Eany%20runs%20for%20penalties%20awarded%20to%20either%20side%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3Eand%20the%20allowance%20for%20the%20boundary%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3Eand%20the%20runs%20completed%20by%20the%20batters%2C%20together%20with%20the%20run%20in%20progress%20if%20they%20had%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3Ealready%20crossed%20at%20the%20instant%20of%20the%20throw%20or%20act.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHarsha%20Bhogle%2C%20the%20commentator%20during%20the%20incident%20on%20Day%201%20of%20the%20first%20Test%2C%20explained%20the%20matter%20on-air%20while%20also%20reminding%20former%20England%20captain%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Eoin%20Morgan%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F833-eoin-morgan-playerprofile%5C%22%3EEoin%20Morgan%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20what%20was%20the%20case%20in%20the%202019%20ODI%20World%20Cup%2C%20contrary%20to%20the%20scenario%20that%20unfolded%20in%20Hyderabad.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706173200000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Ffq89avu8_stokes-and-rehan-afp_625x300_25_January_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Findia-vs-england-2024%2Fwhy-england-were-awarded-5-runs-instead-of-6-despite-batters-running-double-before-overthrow-4-4929187%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22England%20were%20initially%20awarded%206%20runs%2C%20for%20a%20double%20and%20an%20overthrow%204%20during%20the%20Day%201%20of%20the%20first%20Test%20against%20India.%20But%2C%20later%20the%20runs%20were%20reduced%20to%205.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Watch%3A%20Axar%20Patel%20bamboozles%20Jonny%20Bairstow%20with%20a%20beauty%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706172876000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-107140899%2Cimgsize-82406.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Fengland-in-india%2Fwatch-axar-patel-bamboozles-jonny-bairstow-with-a-beauty%2Farticleshow%2F107140946.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22England%20were%2060%2F3%20at%20the%20fall%20of%20Zak%20Crawley's%20wicket%20when