%20of%20the%20Ram%20Temple%20in%20Ayodhya%2C%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20said%20that%20the%20Delhi%20government%20had%20already%20adopted%20the%2010%20principles%20essential%20for%20'Ram%20Rajya'.%20Speaking%20at%20a%20Republic%20Day%20function%20in%20Chhatrasal%20Stadium%2C%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20said%20that%20the%20Delhi%20government%20provides%20good%20education%20and%20health%2C%20pension%20for%20senior%20citizens%2C%20and%20round-the-clock%20power%20supply%20and%20free%20water%20supply.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELord%20Ram%20never%20discriminated%20on%20the%20lines%20of%20caste%20and%20religion%2C%20but%20society%20today%20has%20been%20%E2%80%9Cdivided%20on%20those%20lines%26quot%3B%2C%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EHere%20are%20the%2010%20'Ram%20Rajya'%20principles%20that%20Chief%20Minister%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20claims%20Delhi%20has%20implemented%3A%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E1.%20No%20one%20sleeps%20hungry%20in%20Ram%20Rajya%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EArvind%20Kejriwal%20said%20that%20the%20Delhi%20government%20provides%20free%20rations%20to%20the%20poor%20and%20unemployed%20while%20establishing%20night%20shelters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E2.%20Equal%20education%20for%20all%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%26quot%3BFollowing%20Lord%20Rama's%20example%2C%20where%20both%20kings%20and%20commoners%20studied%20in%20gurukuls%2C%20Delhi%20ensures%20that%20children%20from%20all%20backgrounds%20receive%20the%20same%20education%20in%20government%20schools%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E3.%20Equal%20and%20quality%20healthcare%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20Chief%20Minister%2C%20in%20his%20speech%2C%20highlighted%20how%20Delhi%20has%20improved%20government%20hospitals%20and%20opened%20neighborhood%20clinics%2C%20providing%20free%20medication%20and%20medical%20treatment%20to%20all%20citizens.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E4.%20Free%20electricity%20for%20all%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EWith%20all%20three%20power%20companies%20in%20Delhi%2