%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2024%2Ffilm%2Freviews%2Flook-into-my-eyes-review-1235886893%2Famp%2F%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Admin%2C%20Infrastructure%2C%20Operational%20Woes%20Mount%20as%20JU%20Completes%20Month%208%20Without%20a%20Permanent%20V-C%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F06%2F14164408%2Fjadav-copy.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3EKolkata%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20For%20over%20seven%20months%20now%2C%20Jadavpur%20University%2C%20one%20of%20the%20premier%20educational%20institutions%20in%20India%2C%20has%20been%20in%20a%20state%20of%20flux%20due%20to%20the%20absence%20of%20a%20permanent%20vice-chancellor.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20last%20permanent%20vice-chancellor%2C%20Suranjan%20Das%2C%20retired%20after%20his%20nine-year%20stint%20on%20May%2031%2C%202023.%20West%20Bengal%20Governor%20C.V.%20Ananda%20Bose%2C%20the%20chancellor%20of%20state%20universities%2C%20did%20not%20extend%20his%20tenure.%20Since%20then%2C%20the%20university%20has%20had%20two%20officiating%20V-Cs%2C%20both%20appointed%20and%20then%20dismissed%20by%20the%20Governor.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOfficiating%20V-C%20Buddhadeb%20Sau%20was%20appointed%20by%20Raj%20Bhavan%20on%20August%2017%20last%20year.%20However%2C%20Governor%20Bose%20removed%20him%20on%20disciplinary%20grounds%20on%20the%20eve%20of%20the%20university%E2%80%99s%20annual%20convocation%20on%20December%2023%20last%20year.%20The%20state%20education%20department%2C%20at%20perpetual%20loggerheads%20with%20the%20governor%2C%20reinstated%20Sau%20the%20following%20day%2C%20but%20the%20convocation%20took%20place%20without%20the%20Chancellor%20%E2%80%93%20Governor%20Bose.%20Since%20then%2C%20Sau%20has%20been%20on%20leave%2C%20leading%20to%20a%20suspension%20of%20critical%20academic%20and%20administrative%20matters%20at%20the%20institution.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20following%20was%20posted%20on%20X%20by%20Bengal%20education%20minister%20Bratya%20Basu.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22zxx%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FVm36jMwQrc%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FVm36jMwQrc%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Bratya%20Basu%20(%40basu_bratya)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fbasu_bratya%2Fstatus%2F1738584598937006264%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EDecember%2023%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAmong%20problems%20created%20in%20the%20absence%20of%20a%20permanent%20V-C%20is%20that%20the%20working%20committee%20and%20executive%20council%20could%20not%20meet%20for%20months.%20Signing%20off%20on%20grants%20and%20approvals%20for%20crucial%20research%20work%20are%20also%20stalled.%20Recently%2C%20the%20university%E2%80%99s%20teachers%E2%80%99%20association%20held%20a%20sit-in%20demonstration%20as%20part%20of%20the%20%E2%80%98Save%20JU%E2%80%99%20campaign.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CFinancial%20transactions%20are%20on%20hold%20without%20the%20approval%20of%20the%20vice-chancellor%2C%20putting%20payments%20to%20temporary%20staff%20in%20jeopardy.%20The%20budget%20of%20the%20university%20could%20not%20be%20sent%20to%20the%20state%20government%20this%20time.%20The%20government%20did%20not%20allow%20a%20council%20meeting.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20there%20will%20be%20more%20serious%20problems%20in%20the%20future.%20In%20the%20face%20of%20this%20impasse%2C%20one%20section%20of%20officials%20are%20illegally%20giving%20work%20orders%20to%20their%20preferred%20organisations.%20These%20irregularities%20will%20continue%20until%20a%20permanent%20vice-chancellor%20takes%20charge%2C%E2%80%9D%20alleged%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EPartha%20Pratim%20Roy%2C%20general%20secretary%20of%20the%20Jadavpur%20University%20Teachers%E2%80%99%20Association%20(JUTA).%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGovernor%20Bose%E2%80%99s%20controversial%20decision%20to%20appoint%20interim%20V-Cs%20in%2031%20state%20universities%2C%20including%20Jadavpur%20and%20Calcutta%20University%2C%20without%20consulting%20the%20higher%20education%20department%2C%20has%20triggered%20a%20seemingly%20unending%20conflict%20between%20the%20two%20and%20left%20these%20universities%20without%20permanent%20V-Cs.%20The%20state%20has%20challenged%20this%20move%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20resulting%20in%20a%20further%20delay%20in%20the%20appointment%20of%20permanent%20V-Cs.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMeanwhile%2C%20state-aided%20universities%20in%20West%20Bengal%20are%20under%20scrutiny%20for%20using%20their%20funds%20to%20defend%20Governor%20Bose%20in%20the%20legal%20battle%20with%20the%20state%20government%20over%20V-C%20appointments.%20According%20to%20a%20report%20by%20%3Cem%3ET%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraphindia.com%2Fmy-kolkata%2Fnews%2Fvarsities-legal-expenses-for-bengal-governor-c-v-ananda-bose-to-be-probed%2Fcid%2F1991589%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cem%3Ehe%20Telegraph%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Calcutta%20University%20and%20Jadavpur%20University%20have%20reportedly%20spent%20over%20Rs%2010%20lakh%20and%20Rs%2060%2C000%20respectively%20on%20legal%20matters%2C%20as%20confirmed%20by%20university%20officials.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%20The%20revelation%20has%20prompted%20the%20higher%20education%20department%20to%20set%20up%20a%20committee%20to%20investigate%20the%20%E2%80%9Cjustification%20of%20legal%20expenditure%E2%80%9D%20by%20these%20institutions.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20want%20a%20search%20committee%20to%20be%20formed%20and%20a%20renowned%20academician%20to%20be%20appointed%20as%20V-C.%20The%20future%20of%20students%20is%20in%20question%20due%20to%20the%20ongoing%20conflict%20between%20the%20state%20and%20the%20governor.%20The%20governor%20has%20termed%20the%20convocation%20as%20illegal.%20Now%2C%20if%20he%20cancels%20the%20certificates%20signed%20by%20the%20last%20interim%20V-C%20Buddhadeb%20Sau%2C%20we%20will%20be%20in%20trouble.%20The%20state%20government%20is%20strangely%20maintaining%20silence%20on%20the%20impasse%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Afreen%2C%20a%20student%20of%20the%20University.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEchoing%20Afreen%E2%80%99s%20concern%2C%20Anustup%20Chakraborty%2C%20a%20PhD%20student%2C%20said%20several%20other%20services%20were%20held%20up.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20absence%20of%20a%20permanent%20V-C%20is%20causing%20administrative%20problems%20for%20researchers%20and%20students.%20The%20allocation%20of%20research%20funds%20is%20stuck.%20The%20hostels%20are%20not%20being%20repaired.%20The%20infrastructure%20is%20crumbling.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20no%20secret%20that%20the%20university%20is%20facing%20severe%20financial%20distress.%20It%20has%20only%20a%20third%20of%20the%20funds%20it%20needs%20from%20the%20state.%20Thus%20maintaining%20infrastructure%2C%20providing%20adequate%20resources%2C%20and%20even%20basic%20functionality%20is%20hanging%20by%20a%20thread.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20suspension%20of%20student%20elections%20in%20recent%20years%20has%20also%20posed%20operational%20challenges%20for%20the%20campus%20anti-ragging%20cell%2C%20which%20comprises%20the%20V-C%20and%20elected%20student%20representatives.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELast%20August%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fjadavpur-university-ragging-death-swapnadeep-kundu%5C%22%3Ea%20student%E2%80%99s%20unnatural%20death%20in%20the%20university%20hostel%2C%20allegedly%20due%20to%20ragging%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20had%20sent%20shockwaves%20across%20the%20state.%20Twelve%20current%20and%20former%20students%20of%20the%20university%20are%20currently%20in%20judicial%20custody%20in%20the%20charge%20of%20abetment%20to%20suicide%20of%20a%20minor.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CAfter%20all%20the%20fuss%20about%20ragging%2C%20which%20damaged%20the%20reputation%20of%20the%20university%2C%20what%20will%20happen%20to%20the%20safety%20of%20the%20students%3F%20Can%20only%20CCTV%20solve%20the%20problem%20if%20there%20is%20one%20to%20lead%20the%20university%3F%E2%80%9D%20asked%20Rupam%20Basu%2C%20a%20student%20of%20the%20university.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ETranslated%20from%20the%20Bengali%20original%20by%20Aparna%20Bhattacharya.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706163581000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F06%2F14164408%2Fjadav-copy.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feducation%2Fjadavpur-university-vice-chancellor-governor-cv-ananda-bose%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22'The%20future%20of%20students%20is%20in%20question%20due%20to%20the%20ongoing%20conflict%20between%20the%20state%20and%20the%20governor.'%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A6%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feducation%2Fjadavpur-university-vice-chancellor-governor-cv-ananda-bose%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Why%20butter%20chicken%20is%20at%20the%20heart%20of%20a%20%C2%A3188%2C000%20legal%20battle%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706162100000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F24%2F01%2F70x70%2Fskynews-new-delhi-india-butter_6432523.jpg%3F20240125073456%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fwho-invented-butter-chicken-curry-wars-hot-up-in-india-as-legal-fight-begins-13055862%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22It%20is%20one%20of%20India's%20best-loved%20dishes.%20But%20butter%20chicken%20is%20just%20as%20contentious%20as%20it%20is%20delicious%20-%20with%20two%20Indian%20restaurant%20chains%20locked%20in%20a%20legal%20battle%20over%20claims%20to%20its%20origins.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C