Fpublications%2Fglobal-risks-report-2024%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%C2%A02024%20Global%20Risk%20Report%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20following%20chart%20shows%20the%20varying%20degrees%20to%20which%20misinformation%20and%20disinformation%20are%20rated%20to%20be%20problems%20for%20a%20selection%20of%20analysed%20countries%20in%20the%20next%20two%20years%2C%20based%20on%20a%20ranking%20of%2034%20economic%2C%20environmental%2C%20geopolitical%2C%20societal%20and%20technological%20risks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDisinformation%20is%20defined%20as%20situations%20where%20the%20author%20has%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.apa.org%2Ftopics%2Fjournalism-facts%2Fmisinformation-disinformation%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epurposefully%20sought%20to%20mislead%20their%20audience%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Misinformation%20describes%20information%20which%20is%20spread%20out%20of%20genuine%20belief%2C%20but%20can%20be%20just%20as%20harmful%20%E2%80%93%20like%20is%20sometimes%20the%20case%20with%20conspiracy%20theories.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20is%20the%20country%20where%20the%20risk%20of%20disinformation%20and%20misinformation%20was%20ranked%20highest.%20Out%20of%20all%20risks%2C%20misinformation%20and%20disinformation%20was%20most%20frequently%20selected%20as%20the%20number%20one%20risk%20for%20the%20country%20by%20the%20experts%2C%20coming%20before%20infectious%20diseases%2C%20illicit%20economic%20activity%2C%20inequality%20(wealth%2C%20income)%20and%20labour%20shortages.%20The%20South%20Asian%20nation%E2%80%99s%20next%20general%20election%20is%20expected%20to%20be%20held%20between%20April%20and%20May%202024%20in%20a%20country%20of%20some%201.4%20billion%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFake%20news%20had%20been%20rife%20in%20India%E2%80%99s%202019%20election%2C%20with%20%3Cem%3EVice%3C%2Fem%3E%20reporting%20how%20parties%20had%20%E2%80%9Cweaponised%20the%20platforms%20%5Bof%20Whatsapp%20and%20Facebook%5D%20to%20spread%20incendiary%20m