ight%20the%20party%20that%20has%20harmed%20federalism%2C%20democracy%20and%20harmed%20every%20institution%20and%20she%20will%20not%20step%20back%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Dev.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20addressing%20a%20press%20conference%20in%20Assam%E2%80%99s%20Barpeta%20during%20the%20ongoing%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Nyay%20Yatra%2C%20Congress%20MP%20and%20general%20secretary%20media%20in-charge%20Jairam%20Ramesh%20said%20that%20the%20Congress%20%E2%80%9Ccannot%20imagine%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20without%20Mamata%3Cem%3Eji%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHer%20(Banerjee%E2%80%99s)%20full%20statement%20says%20that%20we%20will%20defeat%20the%20BJP.%20We%20will%20not%20take%20any%20step%20back%20to%20not%20defeat%20the%20BJP.%20We%20are%20entering%20Bengal%20with%20this%20idea.%20When%20you%20are%20on%20a%20long%20journey%2C%20there%20can%20be%20some%20speed%20breakers%2C%20some%20red%20lights.%20This%20does%20not%20mean%20that%20we%20will%20leave%20the%20journey.%20We%20will%20cross%20the%20speed%20breakers%2C%20red%20lights%20will%20become%20green%20lights%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Ramesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20same%20question%20was%20asked%20to%20Rahul%3Cem%3Eji%3C%2Fem%3E%20yesterday.%20And%20he%20said%20that%20Mamata%3Cem%3Eji%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20a%20big%20leader%2C%20of%20India%2C%20of%20Bengal%2C%20of%20the%20TMC%20and%20she%20is%20an%20important%20pillar%20for%20the%20INDIA%20alliance.%20We%20cannot%20imagine%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20without%20Mamata%3Cem%3Eji%3C%2Fem%3E.%20We%20are%20hopeful%20that%20what%20Mamata%3Cem%3Eji%3C%2Fem%3E%20said%20that%20we%20will%20defeat%20BJP%20will%20remain%20the%20idea.%20The%20talks%20are%20on.%20Some%20middle%20path%20will%20emerge%20and%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20will%20fight%20the%20elections%20in%20West%20Bengal%20as%20an%20alliance%20and%20there%20will%20be%20cooperation%20among%20all%20the%20parties.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERamesh%E2%80%99s%20statement%20came%20hours%20after%20Banerjee%20told%20reporters%20that%20she%20will%20go%20it%20alone%20at%20least%20in%20Bengal%20and%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20will%20be%20for%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20had%20given%20them%20a%20proposal%20and%20they%20had%20turned%20it%20down.%20Since%20then%20we%20had%20decided%20that%20we%20will%20go%20it%20alone%20in%20Bengal%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReferring%20to%20the%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Yatra%20which%20will%20enter%20West%20Bengal%20through%20Cooch%20Behar%20on%20Thursday%2C%20Banerjee%20said%20that%20she%20had%20not%20been%20informed%20about%20the%20yatra.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20are%20doing%20a%20yatra%2C%20but%20have%20they%20even%20informed%20me%20even%20once%20that%20we%20are%20coming%20to%20your%20state%3F%20No%20they%20have%20not.%20Hence%20I%20have%20no%20communication%20with%20them%20about%20Bengal.%20We%20will%20think%20about%20what%20to%20do%20or%20not%20to%20do%20on%20an%20all-India%20level%2C%20we%20are%20a%20secular%20party%20and%20we%20will%20do%20everything%20to%20defeat%20the%20BJP.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERamesh%20said%20during%20his%20press%20conference%20that%20the%20Congress%20had%20already%20invited%20all%20INDIA%20alliance%20partners%20to%20the%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Nyay%20Yatra.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CKharge%20(Congress%20president%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge)%20has%20already%20spoken%2C%20Rahulji%20has%20also%20spoken%20about%20it.%20If%20there%20was%20a%20written%20invitation%20I%20will%20check%20and%20let%20you%20know.%20But%20I%20know%20that%20Khargeji%20has%20already%20said%20at%20least%20three%20or%20four%20times%20in%20his%20speeches%20that%20we%20are%20inviting%20all%20INDIA%20alliance%20partners%20and%20he%20has%20spoken%20to%20every%20alliance%20partner.%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20know%20in%20what%20context%20she%20has%20said%20this.%20But%20I%20know%20she%20has%20said%20that%20we%20will%20defeat%20BJP%20and%20with%20this%20idea%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Nyay%20Yat