%20the%20hotel.%20Even%20after%20all%20those%20years%2C%20it%20still%20reminded%20me%20of%20the%20episode%20in%20Mumbai%20when%20my%20legs%20were%20trembling.%20But%20I%20told%20myself%20that%20this%20was%20now%20my%20chance%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20that%20is%20how%20Dev%20debuted%20in%20acting%20with%20a%20TV%20series%20named%20SWAT.%20Today%2C%20he%20is%20one%20of%20the%20most%20successful%20actors%20in%20China.%20His%20journey%20is%20so%20well%20known%20among%20the%20Chinese%20that%20his%20life%20story%20has%20been%20included%20in%20school%20textbooks%20as%20a%20rags-to-riches%20tale%20of%20inspiration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETina%2C%20a%20teacher%20at%20Xi%E2%80%99an%20International%20Studies%20University%20(XISU)%2C%20China%2C%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CDev%E2%80%99s%20story%20has%20a%20very%20important%20impact%20on%20our%20students.%20It%20took%20a%20lot%20of%20hard%20work%20and%20perseverance%20for%20him%20to%20open%20a%20restaurant%2C%20make%20a%20film%20in%20China%20as%20a%20foreigner%2C%20and%20succeed.%20His%20success%20story%20inspires%20young%20children%20to%20have%20the%20courage%20to%20pursue%20their%20dreams%2C%20defy%20difficulties%20and%20keep%20working%20hard.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FDev-Raturi-4-1705931014.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Dev%E2%80%99s%20inspiration%20journey%20is%20taught%20in%20the%20schools%20of%20China%20today.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FDev-Raturi-4-1705931014.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FDev-Raturi-4-1705931014-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FDev-Raturi-4-1705931014-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-