7-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-338664%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EBangaru%20shares%20how%20she%20prepares%20a%20perfect%20potting%20mix%20using%20vermicompost%2C%20kitchen%20waste%20compost%2C%20soil%2C%20cocopeat%2C%20and%20neem%20cake.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhen%20to%20add%20biofertilisers%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20After%20plantation%2C%20Bangaru%20suggests%20adding%20biofertilisers%20and%20liquid%20fertilisers%20in%20the%20pots%20after%20three%20months.%20She%20shares%20the%20composition%20of%20one%20of%20her%20trichoderma-enriched%20biofertilisers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTake%20100%20kg%20of%20cow%20dung%2C%2010%20kg%20of%20neem%20powder%2C%20and%20two%20kg%20of%20trichoderma%20viride.%20Mix%20the%20ingredients%20and%20sprinkle%20some%20water%20over%20it.%20Cover%20it%20with%20a%20cotton%20cloth%20and%20keep%20them%20under%20shade.%20After%20seven%20days%2C%20white-coloured%20good%20bacteria%20will%20have%20formed.%20Then%2C%20directly%20mix%20the%20compost%20with%20cow%20dung%20and%20add%20to%20the%20soil%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAdd%20liquid%20fertiliser%20to%20boost%20yield%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EBangaru%20says%20that%20she%20uses%20a%20unique%20fish%20amino%20acid%20biofertiliser%20that%20promotes%20healthy%20growth%20and%20development%20of%20plants%20by%20regulating%20phototropism%20and%20photosynthesis%2C%20and%20stimulating%20carbon%20and%20nitrogen%20metabolism.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20name%20suggests%2C%20the%20fertiliser%20is%20made%20using%20fish!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fterrac-garden-bangaru-jhansi-5-1705671333.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Bangaru%20prepares%20